
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-cui-netext-lma-redirection-solution-00.txt'>
    <title>"LMA Redirection Solution", Xiangsong Cui</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-cui-netext-lma-redirection-solution-00.txt</link>
    <description>In network-based mobility management domain, LMA is used to manage the mobility of IP node attached to MAG. LMA discovery and LMA redirection mechanism are used to improve the network flexibility. This document is used to introduce a recommended solution for this purpose. In this solution Redirect Agent function is adopted to accomplish the requirement.</description>
    <dc:date>2009-07-26T22:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
